      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW QUINTESSA (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (22.78) in a Mix 6/7 at Ballarat. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. LIVING THE DREAM (4) steps out for the first time at this circuit. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 5 lengths (22.57) at Warrnambool. Expected to feature in the finish. ASTON BONDI (3) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.3 lengths (23.36) behind High Contrast at Warragul. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Expecting another good run. MAISEY MARY (8) deserves plenty of thought at her first run at this circuit.",
